<div id="review_1977230167" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1977230167" />
    <a title="Amit Mishra" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/66799591-amit-mishra"><img alt="Amit Mishra" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1606112214p2/66799591.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1977230167?book_show_action=true">Apr 20, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amit Mishra" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amit Mishra" href="/user/show/66799591-amit-mishra">Amit Mishra</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1977230167" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13317776359546162754">What else could you hope for? The book delivers what it promises - the way of the sparrows are never to be looked in a straight line. The journey of the characters was very vivid and multi-experiencing curve of life. For the best, everyone settles well at the end and the readers are to be left with a pleasure and a sense of satisfaction for the read. Great stuff!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


