<li class='cover' id='bookCover_23301981'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23301981-your-dreams-are-mine-now"><img alt="Your Dreams Are Mine Now" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1412353608l/23301981._SX98_.jpg" />
