<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10826930203757697544">Kartik Sharma, a graduate of Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Delhi and Indian Institute of Management (IIM) Ahmedabad, is passionate about books. Be it reading or writing, he found his one true passion in the written word. <br/><br/>Published at the age of 23 by Rupa Publications in September 2011, he continues to write fiction stories and philosophical musings on his blog: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://interlocutor-kasper.blogspot.in/'>http://interlocutor-kasper.b</a></span>
  <span id="freeText10826930203757697544" style="display:none">Kartik Sharma, a graduate of Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Delhi and Indian Institute of Management (IIM) Ahmedabad, is passionate about books. Be it reading or writing, he found his one true passion in the written word. <br /><br />Published at the age of 23 by Rupa Publications in September 2011, he continues to write fiction stories and philosophical musings on his blog: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://interlocutor-kasper.blogspot.in/">http://interlocutor-kasper.blogspot.in/</a> and also at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://medium.com/@sykartik">https://medium.com/@sykartik</a><br /><br />He quit his investment banking career in 2012 to devote more time to writing. He is currently working on his second novel which he promises to be "fueled with philosophy and at the same time encapsulated in science fiction".</span>
